---
/**
 * Cardiac Services — track page, rebuilt to the visual reference.
 * Deliberately lighter than the imaging track (reference annotation): same
 * panel treatment, same motif, same spacing rhythm — only the content density
 * differs. Hero only, per 3.6's minimal-content decision.
 *
 * Copy is 3.6.1 verbatim as rendered in the reference: positioning line as
 * H1 (mock's line break + no trailing period), three services at equal
 * weight, CTA "Get in touch". No stats row. NO credentials line for now —
 * pending final wording (owner decision; the reference markup that showed
